# Tabs

Use `TxTabs` to switch between related product sections with left, right, top, or bottom navigation. Pair it with `TxTabItem`, optional `TxTabItemGroup`, and optional `TxTabHeader` when the active panel needs contextual chrome.


## Basic Usage

### Tabs
